        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Mother_churches #Other_clerics #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3532">Maifredus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches #Bishops #Monasteries #Archpriests #Prevosts"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1426"><placeName
                                key="#Mother_churches #Bishops #Monasteries #Hospitals #Clusae/gates #Canons"
                                ref="#places/275">Mantuane</placeName> Sedis</orgName> Dei gratia
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> quamvis indignus. Omnibus Mantuanę
                        Ęcclesię clericis et laicis, tam presentibus quam futuris, notum esse
                        volumus quod <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3541">Maifredus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Advocatus #Monks"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2094"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                            Sancti Andreę</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> nostram multotiens adiit clementiam proclamando
                        quod abbas <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Other_clerics"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">monasterii Sancti Benedicti</orgName>
                        iniuste ei detineret <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/2077"
                                ><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitale</rs></orgName> quod bone memorie <rs
                            key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess #Hospitals" ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName>
                        construxit in suburbano Mantuę, situm iuxta <placeName
                            key="#Clusae/gates #Hospitals" ref="#places/275"><rs key="#Clusae/gates"
                                >portam</rs> quę dicitur de Hospitali</placeName>, asserens quod suę
                        ęcclesię deberet esse. Quoniam ergo nostrum est nociva compellere atque
                        lites sedare ad utriusque partis causas audiendas terminum posuimus. Statuto
                        autem die, apud monasterium Sancti Andreę cum <rs key="#Other_clerics"
                            >clericis</rs> ac laicis nostris fidelibus, in claustro affuimus et
                        predictum abbatem Sancti Andreę cum suis fratribus et <persName
                            key="#Advocatus #Monasteries #Witness" ref="#people/3542"
                            >Octone</persName> suo <rs key="#Advocatus">advocato</rs> pluribusque
                        suis fidelibus nec non et <persName key="#Priors" ref="#people/3509"
                            >Ubertum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priorem</rs> cenobii Sancti Benedicti cum suis fratribus
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Heinrico</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Bertram">Bertramro</name></persName> ante nos
                        convocavimus causamque utriusque partis diligenter investigare cepimus.
                        Protulit namque prior Sancti Benedicti <rs key="#Judicial_breve">cartulam
                            qua cognovimus hanc litem sententia</rs>
                        <persName key="#Cardinals #Papal_court_officer" ref="#people/2188"
                            >Bernardi</persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1100">Sanctę Romanę Ęcclesię</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinalis</rs> et domni <persName
                            key="#Popes #Papal_court_officer" ref="#people/52">Pascalis <rs
                                key="#Popes">papę</rs> II</persName> tunc <rs
                            key="#Papal_court_officer">legati</rs>, <rs key="#Witness">presentibus
                            atque confirmantibus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Judicial_breve #Cardinals #Deacons"
                            ref="#people/2173">Pagano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> et cardinale, item domno <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judicial_breve #Bishops" ref="#people/2190"
                            >Ugone</persName> Mantuano episcopo predecessore nostro nec non
                            <persName key="#Witness #Judicial_breve #Abbots" ref="#people/2191"
                            >Airaldo</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2095">Sancti
                            Dionisii <placeName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Witness"
                                ref="#places/147">Mediolanensis</placeName> monasterii</orgName>
                        abbate, <persName key="#Witness #Judicial_breve #Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Villanus">Villano</name></persName>que clerico et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judicial_breve #Judge" ref="#people/2195"
                            >Arderico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudice</rs> ceterisque quam pluribus, coram iam dicta
                        comitissa Matilda fuisse decisam et abbati qui sorte pro tempore fuerit ac
                            <rs key="#Monks">monachis</rs> Sancti Andreę itemque <rs key="#Canons"
                            >canonicis</rs> Mantuanis presentibus pariter et futuris bene vel male
                        in canonica conversantibus huius actionis perpetuum sub excommunicatione
                        silentium esse impositum omnemque eis super hoc ulterius agendo negocio
                        audientiam interdictam, et prefatum hospiciurn cum eiusdem comitissę Matilde
                        consensu ceterorumque supradictorum virorum communi consilio venerabili
                            <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/2189"
                            >Alberico</persName> Sancti Benedicti abbati suisque successoribus fore
                        commissum. Quo audito predictum abbatem Sancti Andreę eiusque monachos quod
                        ad hęc respondere vellent interrogavimus. Ipsi vero nil rationis contra hęc
                        se habere cognoscentes nostro consilio prescripte apostolicę diffinicioni
                        velle obtemperare dixerunt. Nos igitur hac tanta comperta causa atque aliis
                        auditis rationibus, sacrisque inspectis canonibus quibus apostolicis
                        statutis et constitutionibus atque beneficiis non refragandum, potius
                        obtemperandum esse precipitur, supradictę diffinitioni parendum condignum
                        iudicavimus. His actis sepe dictus abbas Maifredus Sancti Andreę cum Attone
                        suo advocato et fratrum suorum presentium communi assensu, in manibus Uberti
                        monasterii Sancti Benedicti prioris sub pena <rs key="#Penalty">C librarum
                            Lucensium</rs> eidem monasterio Sancri Benedicti inferenda pro se
                        successoribus finem faciens exinde huic liti renunciavit. Et ut hoc ab
                        omnibus inviolabiliter observetur nostra episcopali auctoritate censimus ut
                        quicumque hanc litem revolvendo de hinc monasterio Sancti Benedicti super
                        hac re inquietare presumpserit nisi resipuerit anatherna sit. Actum in
                        claustro Sancti Andreę feliciter. Anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi M C XVIIII, indictione XII, VlII kalendas martii. Ego Manfredus Dei
                        gratia Mantuane ecclesię servus subscribo et subscribendo sub
                        excommunicatione confirmo. Ego Manfredus Sancti Andree abbas subscribo et
                        subscribendo excommunicatione confirmo pro me et pro omnibus fratribus. Ego
                        Atto advocatus monasterii Sancti Andree interfui et subscripsi. Ego
                            <persName key="#Archpriests #Witness"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus/archipresbiter">Teodaldus</name></persName> sancte
                        Mantuane ecclesie <rs key="#Archpriests">archipresbiter</rs> licet indignus
                        interfui et subscripsi. Ego <persName key="#Priests #Prevosts #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Hubaldus">Ubaldus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et Mantuane ecclesie <rs key="#Prevosts"
                            >prepositus</rs> interfui et subscripsi. Ego <persName
                            key="#Causidicus #Witness"><name ref="Wido">Wido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> interfui et subscripsi. Intertfuerunt
                        ibi <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Otto/de Mediolano">Octo</name></persName>
                        de Mediolano, <persName key="#childOf #Witness"><name ref="Albertus/de Capite Inicię">Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName> de <placeName>Capite
                            Inicię</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus/Iudeus"
                                >Petrus Iudeus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #Witness"><name ref="Otto/de Gurgolato">Otto</name></persName> de Gurgolato et <persName
                                key="#siblingOf #Witness"><name ref="Wibertus">Guibertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ><name ref="Antelmus">Antelmus</name></persName> item <persName key="#parentOf #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Antelmus">Antelmus</name></persName> et <persName key="#childOf #Witness"
                                    ><name ref="Lanfrancus">Lanfrancus</name></persName> filii eius, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ><name ref="Otto/de Armilina">Otto</name></persName> de <placeName>Armilina</placeName>, <persName
                                key="#Witness"><name ref="Wibertus/Malafinis">Guibertus Malafinis</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                    ><name ref="Azo/Folenga">Azo Folenga</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes/de Frisia">Iohannes</name> de
                            Frisia</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Bonussenior">Bonussenior</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                    ><name ref="Quattromani"></name>Quattuomanus</persName>, <persName key="#Deacons #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes/diaconus de Quistello">Iohannes</name></persName> diaconus de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2417">Custello</placeName>, <persName
                                key="#Other_clerics #Witness"><name ref="Amaldus/clericus Padolironensis">Amaldus</name></persName> et <persName
                                    key="#Other_clerics #Witness"><name ref="Gumbertus/clericus Padolironensis">Gumbertus</name></persName> clerici Sancti
                        Benedicti et plures alii. Ego <persName key="#Other_clerics #Writer"
                            ><name ref="Vitalis/cappellanus">Vitalis</name></persName> domni episcopi Manfredi <rs key="#Chaplain"
                            >capellanus</rs> eius iussu hanc cartulam <rs key="#Writer"
                        >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
